---
// src/components/HowitWorks.astro
---

<section id="how-it-works" class="py-20">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-8">
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-normal font-[Industry] text-pale-turquoise mb-12">
      > Real-World Automation for Your Startup_
    </h2>

    <div class="mb-16">
      <h3 class="text-2xl font-normal text-pale-aqua mb-6">Imagine...</h3>
      <div class="space-y-4 text-lg font-light">
        <p>
          <strong class="text-pale-aqua font-medium"
            >Making your idea come to life</strong
          >, for an affordable price and scaling in mind.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong class="text-pale-aqua font-medium"
            >Deploying new features with confidence</strong
          >, knowing your infrastructure is automated and secure.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong class="text-pale-aqua font-medium"
            >Freeing up your team from repetitive tasks</strong
          > to focus on innovation and user satisfaction.
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong class="text-pale-aqua font-medium"
            >Making data-driven decisions</strong
          > because practical AI is providing actionable insights, not just hype.
        </p>
        <p class="text-pale-aqua font-medium text-xl mt-6">
          Ancillabs builds the systems that make these transformations possible.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="py-5 grid grid-cols-1 gap-10 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-2 ">
      <div class="flex flex-col pr-6">
        <p class="font-semibold mb-2 text-pale-aqua">Problem:</p>
        <p class="font-normal mb-6 text-lg italic">
          "I have a brilliant app idea but no technical co-founder."
        </p>

        <p class="font-semibold mb-2 text-pale-aqua">Ancillabs Solution:</p>
        <p class="font-normal mb-6 text-lg">
          We act as your technical execution partner, guiding you from idea
          validation (Tier 0) through MVP launch (Tier 1) with clear
          communication and no jargon.
        </p>

        <p class="font-semibold mb-2 text-pale-aqua">Benefit:</p>
        <p class="font-normal text-lg">
          Your vision brought to life, technically sound.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col pr-6">
        <p class="font-semibold mb-2 text-pale-aqua">Problem:</p>
        <p class="font-normal mb-6 text-lg italic">
          "Our initial MVP is gaining traction, but it's unstable and hard to
          update."
        </p>

        <p class="font-semibold mb-2 text-pale-aqua">Ancillabs Solution:</p>
        <p class="font-normal mb-6 text-lg">
          We assess your current setup, implement robust DevOps practices,
          migrate you to scalable Infrastructure as Code, and enhance your
          product (Tier 2 or Dedicated Support).
        </p>

        <p class="font-semibold mb-2 text-pale-aqua">Benefit:</p>
        <p class="font-normal text-lg">
          Stable growth, faster iteration, peace of mind.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
